# Keep the Docker build context clean and arch-correct.
#
# .lake/ holds host (macOS) build artifacts — copying them into the Linux build
# would mix architectures. .git and dist/ are build/release noise the container
# build does not need.
.lake/
dist/
.git/
.github/
*.log

# Host (macOS) spike outputs — arch-specific; the Linux build regenerates them.
spike/spike-bin
spike/libkuespike.a
spike/cgo_flags.go
spike/gen/
spike/Spike.c
spike/Spike.o
spike/go.sum
